title: College Football Is Back
description:
Wendi Nix, Harry Lyles Jr., and Ryan McGee react to SEC Commissioner Greg Sankey's comments on Texas and Oklahoma officially joining the SEC in 2025. The crew also take a look at notable Week 1 matchups and make some early predictions for this year's college football season.
